  "description": {
   "en": "A thousand years ago, Lu Lingxi went astray into diabolism, causing a war among thousands of spirits. To stop Lu Lingxi, Mu Feng suffered from soul burning and ended up with both his body and soul destroyed. Lu Lingxi borrowed the Spirit Lantern from Ye Li, the demon leader, to reshape Mu Feng's body, but his soul scattered to the mortal world as the wick broke. Lu Lingxi had no choice but to collect his soul and the wick fragments with young Mu Feng. Unexpectedly, Ye Li and those demons or humans who got wick fragments all seemed to have a strong interest in Lu Lingxi...",
   "es-la": "Hace mil años, Lu Lingxi se involucró en el Cultivo Demoníaco, causando una guerra entre miles de espíritus. Para detener a Lu Lingxi, Mu Feng sacrificó su cuerpo y alma. Lu Lingxi tomó prestada la Linterna Espiritual de Ye Li, el Líder de los Demonios, para devolver el cuerpo a Mu Feng, desafortunadamente su alma se dispersó en el mundo mortal, por lo que Lu Lingxi no tuvo más remedio que bajar, para recolectar los fragmentos Xin (del alma) en compañía del joven Mu Feng. Inesperadamente, Ye Li, demonios y humanos que tienen los fragmentos Xin parecen tener un gran interés en Lu Lingxi..."
  },
